text: Marvel's Jessica Jones is an American TV series and the second Netflix series of the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU), after Daredevil (2015â€“2018). The series was created by Melissa Rosenberg and was on Netflix from November 20, 2015 to June 14, 2019. Krysten Ritter stars in the series as Jessica Jones. The series was produced by Marvel Television. Ritter later returned as the character in The Defenders (2017), a crossover mini series in which Jones teams up with Daredevil, Iron Fist, and Luke Cage. == Cast and characters == * Krysten Ritter as Jessica Jones * Mike Colter as Luke Cage * Rachael Taylor as Patricia "Trish" Walker * Wil Traval as Will Simpson * Erin Moriarty as Hope Shlottman * Eka Darville as Malcolm Ducasse * Carrie-Anne Moss as Jeri Hogarth * David Tennant as Kilgrave * J.
